Coffee is pretty good, and the prices are pretty decent. The place reminds me of an old hole in the wall beatnik coffee house I spent a lot of my highschool and college years in.   I was in there after midnight on a Saturday night, and the atmosphere was pretty relaxing and quiet. Great for when ya need to finish that report or cram for a test.   There's indoor seating, outdoor seating, wifi, private study pods yet they also have a set up for a live band and a drive through for when your on the go. Definately a place that's worth checking out

